---
description: Testing for Next.js frontend
globs:
  - "frontend/**/*.{test,spec}.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use Jest or Vitest with React Testing Library for unit tests.
- Prefer tests that assert behavior, not implementation details.
- Use Playwright for end-to-end tests in `frontend/e2e/`.
- Mock network via MSW in unit tests; avoid real network calls.
- Keep tests fast and deterministic.

